{
  "stem": "7358.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we came-- we came out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody was-- you grow up very quickly in times like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody knew exactly that-- that we are living on borrowed time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard from time to time that liquidation was done in this town, and a liquidation was done in another town, and another ghetto was eliminated.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were always saying that perhaps we will be spared because we are working on the construction of this important road.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So people-- you can talk yourself into all kind of things to-- to try to-- to give you some hope even if it's not real hope.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then on August 26, the-- the-- there was another roundup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we also sl-- had slid into our hiding space, and we were 13 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "13 People.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just barely standing room there because this was-- this-- this was not meant for us to stay longer than a few hours at a time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were all chased out to the square.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we waited an hour, and two hours, and three hours, and four hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the people did not return.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we-- we heard screaming and yelling and-- we knew immediately that this was the final hour of our existence.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we remained hidden in this place for three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was no sanitary condit-- preparations of any kind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no-- no food, no drinking water, just standing-- standing room only.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we definitely knew that this was the final-- the final act because number one, the people never returned back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Number two, the next morning we heard all our Christian neighbors coming into the house and-- and fighting over our possessions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from time to time, we heard shooting and-- and screaming of other people.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
